      color: #16949c;"><a href="https://www.uncoredigital.com" target="_blank">Uncore Digital!</a></span></h2>
      <p>
        Ignitax now focuses on U.S. taxation &amp; accounting, while Uncore Digital handles digital media &amp; social media marketing, website design &amp; development.
        <br/>Please visit Uncore Digital and explore our services.
      </p>
      <a href="https://www.uncoredigital.com" target="_blank" class="popup-btn">Uncore&apos;s website</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  

  